import React from 'react'
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Hero from './Home'
import About from './About'
export default function index() {
  return (
    <>
    <Routes>
      <Route path='/'>
        <Route index element={<Hero/>}/>
        <Route path='about' element={<About/>}/>
        
      </Route>
    </Routes>
    </>
  )
}
